soot.toolkits.graph

Class SimpleDominatorsFinder<N>

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.toolkits.graph.SimpleDominatorsFinder<N>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DominatorsFinder<N>

    public class SimpleDominatorsFinder<N>
extends Object
implements DominatorsFinder<N>
    Wrapper class for a simple dominators analysis based on a simple flow analysis algorithm. Works with any DirectedGraph with a single head.
    Author:
    Navindra Umanee
